citations:
    citation-adwd-the-prince-of-winterfell:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "The Prince of Winterfell"
            text_from_source: "Arya of House Stark comes here to be wed. A woman grown and flowered, trueborn and noble, she comes to beg the blessings of the gods. Who comes to claim her? Me, said Ramsay. Ramsay of House Bolton, Lord of the Hornwood, heir to the Dreadfort."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Ramsay Bolton's wedding ceremony to 'Arya Stark' (actually Jeyne Poole) in Winterfell godswood. Theon gives the bride away. Abel and his washerwoman spearwives present. Northern lords attending: Wyman Manderly, Hosteen Frey, Aenys Frey, Lady Dustin, Whoresbane Umber, Roger Ryswell, Rickard Ryswell, Lord Stout, Lord Locke, and others. Wyman Manderly serves the wedding pies."
